{"type":"article","id":24025,"title":"集中营的诗（2）——哭泣是我们的祷告（三语）","uid":50245,"topics":[1,330,1454,552,163],"contents":"女诗人设定的场景是：一位姐妹在集中营里心脏病发倒下了，难友们都为她哭泣——而哭泣本身，像祷告一样，是被禁止的。现在有三语版了，还缺英文版。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/9bEsAra.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9bEsAra.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9bEsAra.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EhsyWOLXkAANZ-o?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EhsyWOLXkAANZ-o?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EhsyWOLXkAANZ-o?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-09-12","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}